cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV. 

This paper proposes a trajectory generation method for biped walking using a dynamic model of a five link bipedal robot. The focus is on robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY), as the paper deals with generating stable rhythmic gaits for the robot. The method also involves biologically inspired assumptions, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper may also involve machine learning or computer vision techniques for implementing the method, which could fall under cs.LG or cs.CV.
